HEADWORD: Ancony
<hw>An"co*ny</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Origin
unknown.]</ety> <fld>(Iron Work)</fld> <def>A piece of malleable iron,
wrought into the shape of a bar in the middle, but unwrought at the
ends.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

